TextEng: Who are you? What are you doing here?
Text: 넌 누구야? 여기서 뭐 하는 거야?

TextEng: I am <FullName>! Prepare to die, wyrm!
Text: 난 <FullName>이야! 죽을 준비해, 고룡이여!

TextEng: Can I ask you some questions.
Text: 질문 좀 해도 될까?

TextEng: I'll be going now.
Text: 이제 갈게.

TextEng: You've got a real one track mind there.
Text: 정말 한 가지 생각밖에 못 하는구나.

TextEng: Not too bright for a dragon, are you?
Text: 용치고는 별로 똑똑하지 않네, 그렇지?

TextEng: Okay, I'll feed you. Where is your food?
Text: 알았어, 먹이를 줄게. 먹이가 어디 있어?

TextEng: Obviously there's something wrong with you. I'll be going now.
Text: 분명 뭔가 문제가 있구나. 이제 갈게.

TextEng: You're the studpidest dragon I've ever met! I'm out of here!
Text: 내가 만난 용 중 가장 멍청해! 여기서 나갈 거야!

TextEng: I should just kill you and put you out of your misery.
Text: 그냥 죽여서 고통에서 벗어나게 해줄까.

TextEng: Who be you? What you do here?
Text: 너 누구야? 너 여기서 뭐 해?

TextEng: Me am <FullName>! You die now, Dragon!
Text: 나는 <FullName>! 너 지금 죽어, 용!

TextEng: Me want ask question.
Text: 나 질문하고 싶어.

TextEng: Me go now.
Text: 나 간다.

TextEng: Okay, me get it! Dragon hungry! Stop saying 'food!'
Text: 알겠어, 알았어! 용 배고파! '먹이' 그만 말해!

TextEng: You be stupid for dragon. Even me be smart more you.
Text: 너 용치고 멍청해. 나도 너보다 똑똑해.

TextEng: Me feed you. Where be food?
Text: 나 너 먹이 줄게. 먹이 어디 있어?

TextEng: Me smash you, dragon!
Text: 나 너 부숴버려, 용!

TextEng: You crazy, dragon. Me go now.
Text: 너 미쳤어, 용. 나 간다.

TextEng: You too stupid for me! Me go now!
Text: 너 나한테 너무 멍청해! 나 간다!
